
Overview of noun stigma

The noun stigma has 4 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                       
1. stigma -- (the apical end of the style where deposited pollen enters the pistil)
2. mark, stigma, brand, stain -- (a symbol of disgrace or infamy; "And the Lord set a mark upon Cain"--Genesis)
3. stigma -- (an external tracheal aperture in a terrestrial arthropod)
4. stigma -- (a skin lesion that is a diagnostic sign of some disease)
